m/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dragon-age-dreadwolf-2025-release-date-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dragon-age-dreadwolf-2025-release-date-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dragon-age-dreadwolf-2025-release-date-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据一份报告称，由于多次内部延迟， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dragon-age-dreadwolf"><em>《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》</em></a>最终可能会在 2025 年初发布。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dragon-age-writer-mary-kirby-is-one-of-50-bioware-developers-that-have-been-laid-off-3487871">《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》的发行日期、预告片和最新消息</a></strong></li></ul><p>Jeff Grubb 和 Jan Ochoa 在<a href="https://youtu.be/-p_OmY0lUc0">Game Mess Mondays</a> （ <em>Giant Bomb</em>的播客）的一集中谈论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dragon-age-writer-mary-kirby-is-one-of-50-bioware-developers-that-have-been-laid-off-3487871">BioWare 上周发生的裁员事件</a>。大约50名员工被解雇，以确保工作室未来“更加敏捷、更加专注”。</p><p> “有一段时间，我觉得<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dragon-age"><em>《龙腾世纪》</em></a>可能会在今年上映，”格鲁布从自己的消息来源听到这一消息后分享道。 “事实上，在内部，他们一度考虑的日期是下个月——2023 年 9 月。”</p><p> “我认为它很可能会进一步倒退。我预计这款游戏可能会在明年年底推出。”他继续说道，然后补充道，如果开发游戏的方法不发生改变<em>，《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》</em>可能会在 2025 年初发布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3241698" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3241698" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3241698" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Dragon-Age-Dreadwolf.jpg" alt="龙腾世纪恐狼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Dragon-Age-Dreadwolf.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Dragon-Age-Dreadwolf-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Dragon-Age-Dreadwolf-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Dragon-Age-Dreadwolf-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Dragon-Age-Dreadwolf-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Dragon-Age-Dreadwolf-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3241698" class="wp-caption-text">龙腾世纪：恐惧之狼。图片来源：BioWare。</figcaption></figure><p>总经理加里·麦凯表示，解雇员工的决定“非常痛苦”，粉丝们惊讶地发现像玛丽·柯比这样的 BioWare 资深员工也受到了影响。</p><p>格鲁布称，为了弥补损失，<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/mass-effect"><em>质量效应</em></a>团队的成员将被重新分配到<em>恐惧</em>狼。因此，该系列下一场比赛的进展将比预期慢。</p><p> “如果你想知道这一切将如何影响<em>《龙腾世纪：恐惧狼》的开发，</em>请让我明确表示，我们对游戏的奉献从未动摇，”麦凯澄清道。 </p><figure id="attachment_2976363" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2976363" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2976363" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dragon-Age-4@2000x1270.jpg" alt="龙腾世纪：恐惧之狼。图片来源：BioWare" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dragon-Age-4@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dragon-Age-4@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dragon-Age-4@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dragon-Age-4@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dragon-Age-4@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Dragon-Age-4@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2976363" class="wp-caption-text">龙腾世纪：恐惧之狼。图片来源：BioWare</figcaption></figure><p> “我们的承诺依然坚定，我们所有人都在努力让这款游戏配得上<em>《龙腾世纪》</em>的名字。我们相信我们将有足够的时间来确保<em>Dreadwolf</em>充分发挥其潜力。”</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii"><em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em></a> &#39;s first proper patch rolled out on August 25, improving kisses for shorter races and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-kicks-off-short-king-summer-with-patch-notes-too-big-for-steam-3488636">stopping Gale from be